Madonna, 64, has taken to Instagram in a set of stunning snaps as she lay in her bathroom surrounded by mirrors. The star addressed her 18.5 million followers as she shared the shots.   In the pictures, the Holiday hitmaker dazzled in freshly-dyed pink hair and black fishnets.  She appeared to be dressed in a black corset bra in some images, while in others she wore a black and white sweater.  To finish, she accessorised with a crucifix necklace and other silver jewellery around her neck.  The star captioned the post: “Sometimes you just have to lock yourself in the bathroom………”